\caption{Distribution of ENV/LOS strengths for our sample of 3-D mass models. Beams for which the lens galaxy is a member of a group are shown in gray, while non-group lenses are shown in tan. Lenses in groups typically have stronger ENV/LOS contributions than those that are not group members. However, there is substantial overlap so each field needs to be treated individually.}
